title: BRIEF-Discover Financial Reports Credit Card Delinquency Rate Of ‍​1.81 Pct At Jan End Vs 1.72 Pct At Dec End
text: Market News February 15, 2018 / 1:23 PM / Updated 12 minutes ago BRIEF-Discover Financial Reports Credit Card Delinquency Rate Of ‍​1.81 Pct At Jan End Vs 1.72 Pct At Dec End Reuters Staff Feb 15 (Reuters) - Discover Financial Services: * CREDIT CARD DELINQUENCY RATE ‍​1.81 PERCENT AT JAN END VERSUS 1.72 PERCENT AT DEC END * CREDIT CARD CHARGE-OFF RATE ‍​2.17 PERCENT AT JAN END VERSUS 2.13 PERCENT AT DEC END - SEC FILING Source text: ( bit.ly/2o1lJKX ) Further company coverage:
